  "description": "A long exposure nighttime shot showcasing a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline. Two prominent bridges span the water in the foreground, illuminated with strings of lights. The fireworks burst in a cascade of green and white, positioned between the bridges and the city. The city itself is densely packed with buildings, lit up in various colors and creating a luminous backdrop. A tall, slender building with a purple peak stands out amongst the cityscape. The water below is dark and reflects some of the city lights. The overall composition suggests a celebratory event or a special occasion.",
